Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Person A lights a candle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,甲点燃一支蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Its light spreads in all directions
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:05.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,蜡烛的亮光朝各个方向传播
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,forming a bubble that grows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:08.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,形成了一个膨胀的泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Person B only sees the candle light up when he receives the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,乙只有在光线到达后才能看见蜡烛的亮光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or in other words when he enters the bubble
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是他进入这个泡泡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he has seen the candle light up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一旦他看见蜡烛点亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B cannot get out of the bubble
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:20.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他就没法离开这个泡泡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because to do so he would have to exceed the speed of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,除非他比光速更快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the surface of a star emits bubbles of light as time goes by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:30.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝，恒星的表面释放出一个个泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but if the star collapses in on itself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.64,0:00:32.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但如果恒星自身发生坍缩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it can become so compact
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它就可能变得十分密实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that its gravity pulls the fabric of space at the speed of light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:39.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以至于自身的引力以光速使空间收缩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at some point
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在某个时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,its surface emits a final bubble
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:42.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它的的表面释放出最后一个泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which attempts to grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个泡泡试图扩张
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but space contracts the other way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:46.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但空间是向里收缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,such that it remains static
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这样一来，泡泡就会维持静止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,once inside it's impossible to get out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:52.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一旦进入其中，就不可能再出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a black hole
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是黑洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,black holes are bubbles of light frozen by gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:58.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,黑洞是被引力困住的光线泡泡
